      "outlookTitle": "Outlook",
      "outlook1": "Additional EUV equipment activation in Feb is expected to add <strong>+15-20B KRW</strong> in depreciation.",
      "outlook2": "Full-scale HBM3E mass production is expected to increase back-end (assembly/packaging) costs by <strong>8-12% vs Q1</strong>.",
      "outlook3": "Continued wafer price declines will partially offset material cost increases, with overall cost growth rate expected to remain at <strong>2.5-3.5%</strong>.",
      "outlook4": "Legacy products (PC DRAM, NAND) continue to see cost reductions, contributing positively to overall profitability through product portfolio mix effects.",
