      "caution3": "<strong>Structural electricity cost increase:</strong> EUV equipment consumes 10x more power than ArF. Electricity cost surges are inevitable as advanced process share expands.",
      "caution4": "<strong>Labor cost stabilization needed:</strong> Intensifying competition for skilled workers in the semiconductor industry may accelerate labor cost increases going forward.",
